column5: New PB. This is absolutely the biggest fish I have every caught. Normally I fly way up north for this, but funny enough caught it right in front of my house. And yes, it was a musky!
Congrats on a very nice fish, PB's always make an excellent day even better.
It seems that everyone is catching muskie except me this season, lol.    Nice fish!
0/3 this year on musky trips for me.  I would trade 100 pike for 1 musky.  Good fish thou.
Congrats on the PB.  next year he should be even bigger!
big ol head on that thing...nice
great catch,great pic and a great day !
That head is the size of a German Shepherds. She sure is dark. Way to go, and in your back yard to boot.
